data.description:
6.49 Private Acres with a 3-car detached garage, 3 bedroom doublewide manufactured home and storage shed.
The 3-Car Detached 30x30' Garage with a double and one single door, a 2-Car Carport with Storage area. Selling "As Is" where is. three good sized bedrooms and two bathrooms. Buyer is welcome to have inspections done but seller in not making any repairs.  Seller has had a new electric meter base installed. Seller is having the well inspected to make sure it is functioning properly. The Structural Engineering Report has been done. This will need a cash buyer, or a rehab loan.
